body_html: @soumith I have seen that but is there any benchmark numbers available somewhere? We tried the world language model and the speedup was less than 2X. I don't know if that's expected or not. Should we expect the same amount of speedup for the ResNet, AlexNet, and VGG on the ImageNet?
